Name: Summer Paws
About the game: Summer days, warm rain, magical nights! Sleeping kittens are hidden well. Can you find them? Features: 18 handcrafted summer islands with over 100 sleeping cats for you to find and wake up and lots of sea shells to collect so open boxes, search the forests, look inside tents and under umbrellas and solve puzzles charming music no timers, no scores, it's just you and lovely islands and kittens
